name: Genuine Undead Fan art with Artists

metadata.name: Undead Duo
metadata.description:
Fan art of Genuine Undead, featuring two main pillars of Genuine Undead, DocBoom and Maison. DocBoom leading with his wisdom and knowledge while never forget to hold firmly the Green Paper.  
Maison with his Genuine charm and kindness standing steadily in front of the Undead Army.  
Their selflessness, integrity, and compassion are truly remarkable, and they have earned the Undeads' respect and admiration. They lead by example, and their actions speak louder than words.
